<div class="main-content">
    <h1>About Agri-Energy Connect</h1>

    <p>
        Welcome to Agri-Energy Connect, your premier platform for integrating renewable energy and sustainable agriculture. Our mission is to connect farmers and consumers in a way that promotes environmentally-friendly practices while ensuring a robust and reliable food supply chain.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>
        At Agri-Energy Connect, we envision a world where agriculture and energy production are seamlessly integrated to create a sustainable future. By harnessing the power of renewable energy sources such as solar, wind, and biomass, we aim to reduce the carbon footprint of agricultural activities and promote a healthier planet.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
        Our mission is to empower farmers by providing them with the tools and resources they need to adopt renewable energy solutions and sustainable farming practices. Through our platform, farmers can connect with consumers, share their stories, and showcase their products. We believe that by supporting sustainable agriculture, we can make a positive impact on the environment and contribute to the well-being of our communities.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            A marketplace where consumers can browse and purchase products directly from farmers who prioritize sustainable practices.
        </li>
        <li>
            Resources and information on renewable energy solutions tailored for agricultural use.
        </li>
        <li>
            A community platform for farmers to share their experiences, learn from each other, and stay updated on the latest advancements in sustainable agriculture.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>
        Whether you are a farmer looking to adopt more sustainable practices, a consumer interested in supporting local agriculture, or simply someone passionate about the environment, Agri-Energy Connect is the place for you. Join us in our mission to create a more sustainable future for all.
    </p>
</div>
